text: Abaraeus curvidens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1908. It is known from South Africa.BioLib.cz - Abaraeus curvidens. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1908
title: Abaraeus curvidens
